(3811, 43, 'our_story_description', '<b>\r\nEverybody confidently states, “Live in a moment” or “Chase the moment.” We absolutely agree with it.\r\n</b>\r\n\r\nBut there is one thing - the memories are as important as living in a moment. So, we have decided to create something that will remind people of the most beautiful moments in their lives. Something that will immortalize the person, their smile, glance, and emotions.\r\n\r\nThat’s how the idea of charcoal and oil portraits from photo occurred. That’s how we started carrying out our mission by providing original and exceptional gifts.'),
