(3817, 43, 'our_mission_description', 'When it comes to changing the world, some people use the weapon, some use the power, and some go to the rally. Instead, we believe that ART can change the world.\r\n\r\n<b>\r\nPainted Desire philosophy is based on the desire to provide everyone with the memory that will warm their hear\r\n</b>\r\n\r\nWe create handmade portrait gifts from a photo and immortalize the best moment in people’s lives.\r\n\r\nWe want everyone to have an individual high-quality portrait in today\'s time. This kind of gift will always remind you about your loved ones and immortalize special moments in your life.'),
