(4050, 307, 'our_plans_description', 'We want your desire to have a portrait drawn to be fulfilled with high quality and commitment by the best painters in the world.\r\n\r\nWe are building huge plans to conquer the world with art and make each client a bit happier. Portrait from the photo is a unique gift and interesting decoration that brightens up the walls and eyes of the beholder. Every day we make little steps towards our big aim.'),
