(4099, 341, '_our_steps_1_title', 'field_5fb4b24007dec'),
(4100, 341, 'our_steps_1_text', 'The next step will be to upload a photo or several photos you want to be changed into a realistic portrait. Add some comments in case you have some specific wishes (title, sayings, etc.).\r\n\r\nIf you hesitate with what photo to choose, our professional artists will definitely help you to make a choice.'),
(4101, 341, '_our_steps_1_text', 'field_5fb4b25107ded'),
