(4267, 356, 'our_steps_0_title', 'Portrait Characteristic'),
(4268, 356, '_our_steps_0_title', 'field_5fb4b24007dec'),
(4269, 356, 'our_steps_0_text', 'To order the best portrait ever, first, you have to choose the subject - one person, a couple, a pet, landscape, etc. Decide what technique would you like our artist to use to create your portrait: charcoal or oil paints.\r\n\r\nAfter that, choose the preferred size and the background.'),
